entries.femaleVariant: So... Militech made me an offer.
Think I should take it? Should I tell Tom? Feel like I kinda owe it to him – after all, he hired me…
What? Don't be gonk. How much more they offer you?
Sixty?! All right, here's what's gonna happen. You get them to make me the same offer, or I'll tell everyone you contacted Militech. I don't have to remind you what Arasaka does to spies, do I?
What can I say... shoulda kept your mouth shut.
